      <title>西班牙计划缩短工作周，引发企业强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/spanish-government-plans-to-cut-weekly-working-hours-to-37-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府达成协议，将每周工作时间从 40 小时减少至 37.5 小时，因为首相佩德罗·桑切斯 (Pedro Sanchez) 试图利用社会政策，但议会支持率却很低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/spanish-government-plans-to-cut-weekly-working-hours-to-37-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国外长斯塔默在特朗普格陵兰争议中迟迟支持丹麦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/uk-s-starmer-belatedly-backs-denmark-in-trump-greenland-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相的发言人表示，英国首相基尔·斯塔默支持丹麦对格陵兰岛的主权，此前美国总统唐纳德·特朗普重申了美国获得北极岛屿的意图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/uk-s-starmer-belatedly-backs-denmark-in-trump-greenland-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩洛哥工会呼吁十年来首次因工资问题举行总罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morocco-unions-call-first-general-strike-in-decade-on-wage-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩洛哥最大的劳工团体呼吁进行近十年来首次全国性罢工，以迫使总理阿齐兹·阿汉努赫恢复工资谈判并撤销改革该国不完善的养老金制度的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morocco-unions-call-first-general-strike-in-decade-on-wage-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平对特朗普关税的谨慎回应表明中国将面临更多损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新一轮中美贸易战的首轮攻势明确表明，习近平采取了比唐纳德·特朗普第一任期期间更为谨慎的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡什·帕特尔获得 80 万美元特朗普媒体奖引发新冲突问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/kash-patel-s-800-000-trump-media-award-raises-conflict-questions-for-fbi-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡什·帕特尔是唐纳德·特朗普总统挑选的联邦调查局局长，他上周从 Truth Social 母公司获得了价值超过 80 万美元的股票奖励。]]></description>
