      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡对“种族歧视”的商业团体实施管控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/singapore-establishes-controls-on-race-based-business-groups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡议会通过了一项法案，对“基于种族”的商业团体和宗族协会进行控制，旨在维护种族和谐并抑制外国对这个金融中心的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/singapore-establishes-controls-on-race-based-business-groups</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
